# Pizza Sales Dashboard (MS Excel)

## Overview
This project analyzes **48,621 rows of pizza sales transactions Year 2015** to provide insights into revenue, order trends, and customer preferences.  
The dashboard highlights peak sales times, best/worst-selling products, and category performance.  

## Features
- Processed and structured 48k+ rows of transactional data in Excel.  
- Built an interactive dashboard using **PivotTables, slicers, and timeline filters**.  
- Analyzed **daily and hourly sales trends**.  
- Identified top & worst-selling pizzas, category-wise performance, and size distribution.  
- Exported results to a PDF report for quick review.  

## Files
- `Pizza_Sales_Dashboard.xlsx` → Interactive Excel dashboard  
- `Pizza_Sales_Report.pdf` → Static report for review  
